# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

## [0.1.0] - 2025-10-05

### Added
- Initial package structure and core functionality
- `extract_cooccurrence_list()` - Extract pairwise co-occurrence frequencies
- `extract_hoi_list()` - Extract higher-order interaction frequencies
- `calculate_cooccurrence_matrix()` - Convert abundance to occurrence matrices
- `delta_cooccurrence_random_model()` - Random null model for statistical testing
- `delta_cooccurrence_permutation_model()` - Permutation null model for statistical testing
- `delta_hoi_random_model()` - Random model for higher-order interactions
- `delta_hoi_permutation_model()` - Permutation model for higher-order interactions
- `construct_network_delta()` - Build differential co-occurrence networks
- `construct_hoi_diagram()` - Create higher-order interaction diagrams
- `plot_cooccurrence_network()` - Network visualization using ggplot2
- `plot_cooccurrence_heatmap()` - Abundance heatmaps using pheatmap
- `plot_differential_summary()` - Summary plots of differential analysis
- `validate_occurrence_matrix()` - Data quality validation
- `differential_cooccurrence_analysis()` - Main wrapper function for complete workflow
- Comprehensive vignette with examples and methodology explanation
- Unit tests using testthat framework
- Documentation using roxygen2
- Package infrastructure (DESCRIPTION, NAMESPACE, README)

### Dependencies
- Core: igraph, network, pheatmap, ggplot2, zCompositions, stats, utils
- Suggested: GGally, dplyr, ggpubr, testthat, knitr, rmarkdown

### Documentation
- Complete function documentation with examples
- Comprehensive vignette tutorial
- README with quick start guide
- MIT license

